{
  "stem": "7414.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he had a pond which was frozen stiff in the winter.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he built a shack over there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So we were going there to skating.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "There, the few kilometers, skating there, and back the few kilometers.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So it was rather fun, because we were all young and healthy, and, you know, and it was much nicer than sit always in the center of the, of the town.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So, we stayed-- as I told, we, I stayed at home until 1939.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My eldest sister was by then married, and she lived with her family in another town, most to the east in Ukrainian part.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My brother married, stayed in Przemysl.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Joseph stayed in Przemysl.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He married, had a child, and was in business.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Rosa came back from her study and the problem started all over again, because she could not practice medicine in Prague.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "She had to sign that she's, she's not going to stay there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Yes?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But when she come to Poland, she was not allowed, because she had a foreign diploma.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There was a possibility to get through a special exam at the university, but the Jews were not admitted.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Even when my father wanted to pay and to bribe or something, it could not be-- just was not done, not at this time, anymore.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So she stayed at home, and she married.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In '38, she married.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And, that was-- and David was, of course, in France.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the youngest was everywhere, because he was so undisciplined [LAUGHS] that he was, was sent from one school to another all over Poland.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And so I was the only one stayed, which stayed at home.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "By then, I was in close friendship.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I met my husband, future husband, and we had a very nice group, this young people.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
